data.description: 3356 SQUARE FEET!! YOU WILL FALL IN LOVE WITH THIS 5BED/3BATH HOME WITH TONS OF UPGRADES!! Better then new!! Open concept floorplan with plenty of space for everyone.   As you enter you are greeted with the perfect guest bedroom or office with a full bathroom.  Open living room, dining room and kitchen. Plenty of cabinets and counter space with an oversized island.  Spacious mud room and walk in pantry. Hardwoods throughout the main area.  Huge media room upstairs, oversized secondary bedrooms with plenty of closet space.  Split bedroom plan with master on one side of the home, upgraded vanities in all the bathrooms, large laundry room, and more closets then you will see in most homes for all your storage needs.  Upgraded covered back patio that is screened in and extra concrete on the side to enjoy the outdoors.  Fenced in backyard.  You will love all the upgrades and details of the home from the the epoxy on the garage floor, hardwired speakers in the ceiling, and upgraded appliances.  Great location close to Harbins park and shopping.  Enjoy the neighborhood pool and playground.
